@page "/"

<PageTitle>Spillgebees.Blazor.Map</PageTitle>

<div class="doc-hero">
    <div class="doc-hero-brand">Spillgebees</div>
    <h1 class="doc-hero-title">Blazor.Map</h1>
    <p class="doc-hero-tagline">A Blazor component library for interactive maps powered by MapLibre GL JS.</p>
    <div class="doc-hero-actions">
        <a href="installation" class="doc-hero-cta-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="components/sgb-map" class="doc-hero-cta-secondary">See Examples</a>
    </div>
</div>

<h2>Features</h2>

<div class="doc-cards">
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Vector &amp; Raster Tiles</h3>
        <p>OpenFreeMap presets work out of the box with no API key. Also supports WMS, WMTS, ArcGIS MapServer, and any custom MapLibre style URL.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Markers &amp; Shapes</h3>
        <p>DOM-based markers with drag support, GPU-rendered circles and polylines, and programmatic or marker-anchored popups.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Real-Time Tracking</h3>
        <p><code>SgbMap.TrackedDataLayers</code> manages moving entities with smooth updates, path decorations, and built-in clustering.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Style Composition</h3>
        <p>Compose multiple MapLibre styles. Layer a base map with one or more overlay styles, each with their own sources and layers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Interactive Legends</h3>
        <p>Toggleable legend control with fully customisable item templates, wired to layer visibility groups.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-card">
        <h3>Dark Mode</h3>
        <p>Light and dark themes for UI controls, navigation, scale bar, popups, and attribution, independent of map tile styling.</p>
    </div>
</div>
